00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:41,360
 Versus cash payments, uh, in the, uh, total number of transactions.

342
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:48,360
 First, uh, the question for, uh, miss, uh, Simon from, uh, Banka Slovenia.

